STATE of North Carolina
v.
Chad Aaron JOHNSON. No. 4P07-2. Supreme Court of North Carolina. December 11, 2008. Bruce T. Cunningham, Jr., Southern Pines, for Chad Aaron Johnson. Amy Kunstling, Assistant Attorney General, Jeff Hunt, District Attorney, for State of NC.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed by Defendant on the 8th day of September 2008 in this matter for a writ of certiorari to review the order of the Superior Court, Transylvania County, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court of that County:

"Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 11th day of December 2008."
